# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Flint Forge — .gitignore
#
# Policy: KBD orchestrator state is TRACKED, not ignored.
# The `.kbd-orchestrator/` tree (project.json, waypoints, phase
# assessments/goals/plans/progress/handoffs) and the KBD event
# log under `.prometheus/` are the durable, file-based source of
# truth for the development process and MUST be committed.
# See CLAUDE.md §"No Hidden State".
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Rust / Cargo ──
/target/
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.cwasm

# pgrx build artifacts (Flint Anvil extensions)
/.pgrx/
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll

# ── Dagger cache ──
/.dagger/.cache/

# ── Environment / secrets ──
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Scaffold / research scratch (not project source) ──
_scaffold.py
.firecrawl/
.meta_html_body.txt

# ── IDE ──
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml

# ── OS ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Agent-tool state
#
# Shared, checked-in assets (commands/, skills/, agents/) stay
# tracked so every tool has the same project context. Only the
# machine-local scratch is ignored.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/settings.local.json
.opencode/opencode-loop/
.kbd-orchestrator/*.local.json

# ── KBD state: keep everything (explicit un-ignore guard) ──
!.kbd-orchestrator/
!.kbd-orchestrator/**
!.prometheus/
!.prometheus/**
